			&nbsp;









LODSB


No operands


Load byte at DS:[SI] into AL. Update SI.Algorithm:



AL = DS:[SI]
if DF = 0 then
	
	SI = SI + 1
	
	else
	
	SI = SI - 1
	



Example:


ORG 100h

LEA SI, a1
MOV CX, 5
MOV AH, 0Eh

m: LODSB
INT 10h
LOOP m

RET

a1 DB 'H', 'e', 'l', 'l', 'o'



 C Z S O P A 
 unchanged 


TOP
